- List a forked coin on any exchange
- Use QNT's XMSS-PoUW integration in a commercial product

## Why BSL?
QNT is the world's first Proof-of-Useful-Work (PQ-PoW) cryptocurrency,
secured by XMSS post-quantum cryptography (NIST-approved).
We open our code for transparency and security audits — not to be copied.
On June 15, 2030, this license converts to GPL-2.0 for the world to use freely.

